da: Er du tilbage igen for at få råd om omverdenen?

...Hvem narer jeg?
Du er eventyreren her, ikke mig!
Så du er måske her for at få råd om <c=cardinal>den fyr</c>, <w>hmmm?</w>
en: Back again for advice on the outside world?

...Who am I kidding?
You're the venturer here, not me!
Then, perhaps you're here for advice on <c=cardinal>that guy</c>, <w>hmmm?</w>
es:
...¿A quién quiero engañar?
¡Tú eres la aventurera aquí!
